{% extends 'base.html.twig' %}
{% block content %}
<div class="container">
    <h1 class="book-title">About Us</h1>
    <section>
        <p>Welcome to our website! We are an online platform that offers a vast collection of books for readers of all genres. Our goal is to provide a seamless and enjoyable reading experience for book enthusiasts.</p>
        <p>With our website, you can easily search for books, access their basic information such as title, author, and synopsis, and even apply various filters to refine your searches. This helps you discover new books that match your interests and preferences.</p>
        <p>In addition to browsing and exploring books, you can create a personalized profile on our platform. Your profile allows you to keep track of your favorite books by adding them to your liked list. This feature helps you curate a collection of books that you love and want to revisit in the future.</p>
        <p>Furthermore, our platform fosters a vibrant reading community. You can engage with other users by adding comments and sharing your thoughts about specific books. It's a great way to connect with fellow readers, exchange recommendations, and participate in meaningful discussions about the literary world.</p>
        <p>We are continuously improving our platform to enhance the user experience. Currently, we are working on developing a chat and meetup function, which will allow users to interact in real-time, engage in book-related conversations, and even arrange meetups with like-minded readers.</p>
        <p>Thank you for being a part of our reading community. Happy reading!</p>
    </section>

    <div class="subcontainer">
        <section>
            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p>Welcome to our website! We are an online platform dedicated to fostering a love for reading and connecting book enthusiasts worldwide.</p>
            <p>Our mission is to provide a comprehensive and user-friendly platform that empowers readers to discover, explore, and engage with a wide range of books. We strive to make the reading experience enjoyable, convenient, and personalized.</p>
            <p>We are committed to curating a diverse collection of books, ensuring that readers can easily find titles across various genres, authors, and themes. Our platform offers powerful search and filtering capabilities, allowing users to find their next favorite book with ease.</p>
            <p>At the heart of our mission is the desire to build a vibrant reading community. We aim to create an inclusive and supportive space where readers can connect, share their passion for books, exchange recommendations, and engage in meaningful conversations.</p>
            <p>As we continue to develop our platform, we prioritize user feedback and continuously improve our features to meet the evolving needs of our community. We are dedicated to enhancing the reading experience and providing a platform that inspires and enriches the lives of book lovers.</p>
            <p>Join us on this literary journey and be a part of our mission to spread the joy of reading!</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Our Values</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Passion for Reading:</strong> We have a genuine passion for books and believe in the transformative power of reading. We strive to ignite and nurture this passion within our community.</li>
                <li><strong>User-Centric Experience:</strong> Our users are at the heart of everything we do. We are committed to providing an exceptional user experience, continuously improving our platform based on user feedback and needs.</li>
                <li><strong>Curated Selection:</strong> We carefully curate our book collection, ensuring a diverse range of titles across genres, authors, and themes. We believe in promoting inclusivity and providing options that cater to a wide range of reading preferences.</li>
                <li><strong>Community Engagement:</strong> We foster a vibrant and supportive community of readers. We encourage active participation, dialogue, and the sharing of ideas, recommendations, and insights among our users.</li>
                <li><strong>Quality and Trust:</strong> We prioritize quality in everything we offer, from book recommendations to user-generated content. We strive to build trust with our community by providing accurate information and maintaining a safe and respectful environment.</li>
                <li><strong>Innovation and Growth:</strong> We embrace innovation and continuously seek new ways to enhance the reading experience. We are committed to staying up-to-date with emerging technologies and trends to provide cutting-edge features and services.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>These values guide us in our mission to create an engaging and enriching platform for readers worldwide. We invite you to join our community and experience the difference!</p>

        </section>
    </div>

</div>


{% endblock %}
